15:- <span style="color:#c77dff;">ENABLE_FFPA_ALL_STAGES</span>, default `True (1)`, When `1`, generate kernels for all multi-stage variants (stages `1~4`); when `0`, only stages `1~2` are generated. Reducing this shortens build time at the cost of fewer schedule choices at runtime.
37:- <span style="color:#c77dff;">ENABLE_FFPA_FORCE_QK_F16</span>, default `False (0)`, Force `Q@K^T` MMA accumulator to FP16 within the FFPA Acc-F32 kernels. Enables the mixed mode `Q@K^T MMA Acc F16 + P@V MMA Acc F32`.
38:- <span style="color:#c77dff;">ENABLE_FFPA_FORCE_PV_F16</span>, default `False (0)`, Force `P@V` MMA accumulator to FP16 within the FFPA Acc-F32 kernels. Enables the mixed mode `Q@K^T MMA Acc F32 + P@V MMA Acc F16`.
47:- <span style="color:#c77dff;">ENABLE_FFPA_SMEM_SWIZZLE_Q</span>, default `True (1)`, `True`: bank-conflict-free Q SMEM via swizzle. `False`: bank-conflict-free via padding.
